        public void drawWeaponCard​(WeaponCard drawn,

                           WeaponCard toRelease)
        Pays the draw price of the card and adds it to the weapons list
        Parameters:
        drawn - the card to draw
        toRelease - the card to release to grab the new one. Can be null unless you already have 3 weapons
        Throws:
        TooManyCardsException - if you have 3 cards in your hand and toRelease is null
        CheatException - if you do not have the card toRelease

      • playPowerUp

        public void playPowerUp​(PowerUpCard powerUpCard,
                        Ammo ammo,
                        PowerUpCard paymentPowerUpCard)
        Activated the powerup card given as param paying the ammo, if it costs
        Parameters:
        powerUpCard - the card to activate
        ammo - the cube you are paying to activate it. could either be null
        paymentPowerUpCard - the powerup card you are using to pay for the activation of this card if the card is free or one (and only one) of the colors should be set to 1
        Throws:
        WeaponCardException - if you cannot activate it
